# Content engine context

- **Production validation:** `docs/CONTENT_ENGINE_PRODUCTION_VALIDATION.md` — dedupe, quality filter, skip > weak output, `RUN_META.md` **Generation status** (`completed` \| `skipped`).
- **Priority:** MESSAGE > VOICE > DESIGN (`docs/MESSAGE_SYSTEM.md`).
- **Voice / QA:** `newsletter/style/jackye-voice.md` (mission-anchored, radically inclusive, **mirror** reader, customize with real signals only), `newsletter/style/enforcement.md`.
- **News / sourcing:** `newsletter/WDIWF_NEWS_CHARTER.md`.
- **Visuals (guides only):** `docs/visual-references/README.md`, `docs/VIRAL_POSTER_IMAGE_SPEC.md`.
- **Product facts:** `docs/BUILD_BIBLE.md` — do not promise unverified features.

Bi-hourly (**`HOT_SIGNAL_ENGINE`**) and Friday (**`FRIDAY_NEWSLETTER`**) procedures live in `automations/HOT_SIGNAL_ENGINE.md` and `automations/FRIDAY_NEWSLETTER.md` (see `automations/AUTOMATIONS_REGISTRY.md`). Outputs go under `newsletter/outputs/live/run-*` and `newsletter/outputs/friday/run-*`. **Do not enable** Cursor automations until `docs/CONTENT_ENGINE_PRODUCTION_VALIDATION.md` passes.

If inputs are missing or publishing credentials are absent, write **blockers** — do not fabricate content.
